metadata.name: The commune
metadata.description: Coming together has been one of the greatest secrets to growth, as an individual who believes in people I have been able to associate with different people around me. met people who love to have fun met the shy, confused, happy, stoners, introvert, ambivert, older, married, single different ethnicity but we all share a common goal which is growth this piece is my community piece,  appreciating does who connect with you.
